Deliverables

Claude must generate all files needed so the project runs with:
    •    React 18 + TypeScript (strict mode)
    •    Vite as bundler
    •    ESLint + Prettier + Husky + lint-staged
    •    Jest + React Testing Library (unit tests)
    •    Playwright (E2E tests)
    •    GitHub Actions CI/CD (lint → test → build → coverage)
    •    PWA readiness (service worker scaffold, manifest.json, offline.html)
    •    Secure .env setup (.env.example, .gitignore)
    •    Docs: README.md, docs/ARCHITECTURE.md, docs/TEST-REVIEW.md
    •    Rules: .cursorrules, claude.rules/

